<h2>4. You can do anything for 10 seconds
</h2>

<p>If you find the task difficult to do, set yourself timed goals. Some people like pomodoro timers, which are timers for 20 minutes. These can help focus our mind, and dedicate a slice of time to doing our thing.
</p>

<p>Try to do as much of your thing in 20 minutes, and then have a break.
</p>

<p>If 20 minutes is too long, try 10 seconds. You could have a break after, or try another 10 seconds.
</p>

