<h2>5. Acknowledge your wins
</h2>

<p>Sometimes we can forget how capable we are. This can set us up thinking that we can’t do our thing, when that isn’t true. To get around this, think back to challenges that you have had and that you’ve overcome.
</p>

<p>It can be big or small. Whatever it is, it’s about remembering that you have overcome difficulties and can do so again!
</p>

<p>You are brilliant, and you can do your thing!
</p>

